{{Infobox person | name = Aban Pestonjee | image = Aban_Pestonjee_-_chairperson_of_Abans_Group.jpg | image_size = | caption = | birth_name = | birth_date = | birth_place = | residence = [[Colombo]], [[Sri Lanka]]. | nationality = | ethnicity = | alma_mater = | occupation = [[Entrepreneur]] <ref>{{cite web|title=Aban Pestonjee – Entrepreneur|url=http://zoroastrians.net/2008/01/04/aban-pestonjee-entrepreneur/|publisher=www.zoroastrians.net|accessdate=26 June 2013}}</ref> | known_for = Chairperson of Abans group of Companies <ref>{{cite web|title=The life-force behind Abans|url=http://www.island.lk/2002/03/10/leisur01.html|publisher=Official website of The Island News Paper, Sri Lanka|accessdate=26 June 2013}}</ref> | salary = | networth = | title = | spouse = P.N.Pestonjee | children = Saroshi, Behman, Rusi | signature = | signature_alt = | website = http://abansgroup.com }}
'''Aban Pestonjee''' ({{lang-si|අබාන් පෙස්ටොන්ජි}}), the [[Chairman|chairperson]] and founder of the Abans group of companies and known as one of the first [[entrepreneur]]s who initiated in first bringing [[Korea]]n [[technology]] to [[Sri Lanka]]n consumers.
== Personal life ==
Pestonjee is part of the [[Parsi]] community.
{{Empty section|date=November 2014}}
== Business Life == She started off her business in 1968 in her home garage where she managed to restore the used appliances which she acquired from auctions and home sales to better working condition and sell them at her corner shop in Galle road.
In 1978, the [[economy]] opened up and there was a huge inflow of imported products. This led to an increased demand from the customers for quality global brands. First, she imported products from [[England]], then from [[Thailand]], [[China]], [[Japan]] and [[Korea]].
Abans Group is mainly divided into 5 business categories such as retail, services,<ref>{{cite web|title=Abans retail|url=http://buyabans.lk/|accessdate=27 June 2013}}</ref> logistics, manufacturing and real estate and infrastructure development under which come Abans (Pvt) Ltd, Abans automobile,<ref>{{cite web|title=Abans Automobile Division |url=http://www.abansgroup.com/loader/page/automobile/index |publisher=Abans Group official website |accessdate=27 June 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130704021256/http://www.abansgroup.com/loader/page/automobile/index |archivedate=4 July 2013 }}</ref> Abans ABSTRACT,<ref>{{cite web|title=Abans Group - Abstract |url=http://www.abansgroup.com/loader/page/aworld/index |publisher=Abans Group official website |accessdate=27 June 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130629155333/http://www.abansgroup.com/loader/page/aworld/index |archivedate=29 June 2013 }}</ref> S.A. Electricals (Pvt) Ltd Services, Abans Central AC Division, Abans Finance,<ref>{{cite web|title=Abans Finance|url=http://www.abansfinance.lk/|accessdate=26 June 2013}}</ref> Abans Tours,<ref>{{cite web|title=Abans Tours|url=http://abanstours.lk/|accessdate=26 June 2013}}</ref> AB Securities (Pvt) Ltd etc.
== Awards and honours == * The Award of Excellence for Woman Achievers for Outstanding Achievement from the SAARC Women’s association in Year 2000.<ref name="Pestonjee">{{cite web|title=Aban Pestonjee|url=http://www.slbo.lk/investcse/forum/viewtopic.php?f=11&t=43|publisher=Invest CSE website|accessdate=26 June 2013}}</ref> * “The Bronze Award” for the Large Business Category by the Women’s Chamber of Industry & Commerce at the Year 2000 Women Entrepreneurs of the Year Award Ceremony.<ref name="Pestonjee" /> * “KOTRA Plaque of Appreciation -- 2005” for forging strategic foreign economic ties between Korea & Sri Lanka presented by Mr. Young Kyo, president and CEO of the [[KOTRA]](Korea Trade Promotion Agency).<ref>{{cite web|title=Aban Pestonjee receives 'Kotra' plaque|url=http://www.sundayobserver.lk/2005/01/23/bus12.html|publisher=Official website of Sunday Observer news paper, Sri Lanka}}</ref> * In 2006, she received International Recognition for winning the Leading Women Entrepreneur of the World award.<ref>{{cite web|title=Women Entrepreneurs Award for Abans Chief |url=http://www.dailynews.lk/2006/03/20/fin07.asp |publisher=Official website of Daily News paper, Sri Lanka |accessdate=26 June 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080524075352/http://www.dailynews.lk/2006/03/20/fin07.asp |archivedate=24 May 2008 }}</ref> Mrs. Pestonjee was awarded the prize by the Princess of [[Thailand]]. * She also received the [[LG Corp|LG]] award for the Best Importer on [[Southeast Asia|South-East Asia]] on behalf of Abans Limited.<ref>{{cite web|title=Abans awarded Best LG Importer in SouthEast Asia|url=http://www.island.lk/2006/11/18/business7.html|publisher=Official website of the Island paper, Sri Lanka}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Abans awarded best LG importer in South-east Asia|url=http://www.nation.lk/2006/11/19/busi8.htm|publisher=www.nation.lk/|accessdate=26 June 2013}}</ref>
